PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777299067
OL,3,CWhy do people stalk? From 'goal
OL,4,Corientation' to 'addiction'
OL,6,F"We think, for a particular profile of
OL,7,Fstalker, the dopamine hits for them
OL,8,Fare so big it can be equated to an
OL,9,Faddiction."
OL,11,FPsychologists and experts in the field
OL,12,Foften class stalking by five different
OL,13,Fcategories based on the motivation
OL,14,Fbehind the behaviour. Those five
OL,15,Fcategories are:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
