OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777299067
OL,3,CWhy do people stalk? From 'goal
OL,4,Corientation' to 'addiction'
OL,6,FInterventions Alliance are a team of
OL,7,Fprofessionals who create intervention
OL,8,Fprogrammes to address behavioural
OL,9,Fchallenges.
OL,11,FAmong their work is the Compulsive
OL,12,FObsessive Behaviour Intervention
OL,13,F(COBI), an intensive programme
OL,14,Fdesigned for individuals exhibiting
OL,15,Fobsessive and controlling behaviours,
OL,16,Fsuch as stalking and harassment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
