FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777299067
OL,3,CWhy do people stalk? From 'goal
OL,4,Corientation' to 'addiction'
OL,6,FMichael Baker, Deputy Chief Executive
OL,7,Fand lead for Research and
OL,8,FCommunications at Interventions
OL,9,FAlliance, said for the programme to be
OL,10,Fsuccessful it was crucial to
OL,11,Funderstand the typology behind the
OL,12,Fstalker.
OL,14,FHe told ITV News: "It's really
OL,15,Fimportant to understand the
OL,16,Fmotivations of a stalker to be able to
OL,17,Ftreat them effectively.
OL,19,F"You have to understand the causes of
OL,20,Fthe motivations of the stalker before
OL,21,Fyou can tackle the behaviour."
OL,26,@vD@SOU{D@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
