PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777299067
OL,3,CWhy do people stalk? From 'goal
OL,4,Corientation' to 'addiction'
OL,6,FHis message to anyone recognising
OL,7,Fthese behaviours in themselves was to
OL,8,Fseek help to change their behaviour.
OL,10,FHe said: "Sometimes people know that
OL,11,Ftheir behaviour is wrong and they
OL,12,Fwould like to get help.
OL,14,F"And there is, in some parts of the
OL,15,Fcountry, help available and I would
OL,16,Fencourage you to look at your police
OL,17,Fand crime Commissioner website.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
