OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1777299067
OL,3,CWhy do people stalk? From 'goal
OL,4,Corientation' to 'addiction'
OL,6,F"I think we should encourage people to
OL,7,Fself-refer to these kinds of programs
OL,8,Fas well, because there is funding out
OL,9,Fthere for people who know they need
OL,10,Fsome help."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
